> The windshield wipers on my 76 westy quit working .They are stuck in the up position and wont go back down to where they normally rest.When I hit the switch I can hear a motor running.Any ideas about whats broke?

there is a gear on a shaft that on mine came loose, I repaired it by
stuffing it full of epoxy and shredded steel wool.

clean up the steel wool leftovers and let dry full time reccommended
plus.

mine lasted several years until I could find a full replacement

YMMV

